structure.unit: LICENSING OF MOTOR VEHICLES, OPERATORS, AND TRAILERS

law.history: Repealed 2005 Ky. Acts ch. 133, sec. 11, effective June 20, 2005. -- Amended 2003 Ky. Acts ch. 74, sec. 2, effective June 24, 2003. -- Created 1996 Ky. Acts ch. 366, sec. 1, effective July 15, 1996.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Application for special license plates pursuant to KRS 186.186 to 186.1867 -- Vehicles leased or provided pursuant to an occupation -- Renewal, fees, administrative regulations.
